Package: SMCReichbR
Title: SMC Tools for Krankenhaus Erreichbarkeitsanalysen
Version: 0.0-3
Authors@R: 
	person("Simon", "Essink", email="simon.essink@sciencemediacenter.de", role=c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1390-3885"))
Description: Provides tools for accessing the Science Media Center (SMC) hospital
    driving time database and performing hospital accessibility analyses
    (Erreichbarkeitsanalysen). Functions are included to connect to PostgreSQL and
    DuckDB databases, load and transform geospatial data, apply geographic filters,
    and export summaries for downstream reporting and visualization.
